  tests/libtest/lib1545.c:38:3: error: 'curl_formadd' is deprecated: since 7.56
  .0. Use curl_mime_init() [-Werror=deprecated-declarations]
     38 |   curl_formadd(&m_formpost, &lastptr, CURLFORM_COPYNAME, "file",
        |   ^~~~~~~~~~~~
