  These dependencies are now already included in the Docker image.

  Ref: https://github.com/mback2k/curl-docker-winbuildenv/commit/2607a31bcab544
  b41d15606e97f38cf312c1ce56

  Closes #11889

Daniel Stenberg (19 Sep 2023)

